{"tid":2419383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"第一滴血： 選舉事務處文書主任確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2021-02-23T09:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T09:46:04.000Z","uid":230530,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a32775096039b9f5b699d2ff800723db2ed27e10","tid":2419383,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"選舉事務處一名文書主任，確診新型冠狀病毒病，已入院接受治療；患者於九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓上班，負責選民登記後勤工作，辦公室不對外開放，他昨日有返工，工作時一直有佩戴口罩，體溫正常。選舉事務處下午已關閉涉及的辦公室，徹底清潔消毒，設於同層的查詢櫃位及選舉資訊中心亦會暫停服務，直至另行通知。由於查詢熱線組的工作地點亦屬同一樓層，因此選舉事務處電話查詢服務亦受到影響，只能維持有限度服務。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380218&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3xPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=c67f5b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380218</a>"},{"pid":"1e07198bc69d547d4c82955ad69857d4d18124f7","tid":2419383,"uid":275238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jE6dtzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjE6dtzj.gif&h=0239e41e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a2d185ce96962bb7b796034904c9c2c48e2fa39","tid":2419383,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"師傳又中"},{"pid":"9d0017a5c420df524864d0c2687a40307cae5a48","tid":2419383,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"GOOD"},{"pid":"f91bb8e55eba1d084c7f769328f1c4edf74cdb0a","tid":2419383,"uid":390224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"嘟咗安心出行唔係有金剛不壞之身嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}